Package com.programmerdan.minecraft.civspy.listeners.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BreakListener
    Sample Listener class that records all block breaks for summation by who and what.
    BucketListener
    player.bucket.empty and player.bucket.fill includes player and nature of bucket
    CitadelListener
    Sample Listener class that records all citadel damage and break for summation by who and what.
    CombatListener
    Records the nature of combat damage issued as delivered by players.
    ConsumeListener
    Contributes player.consume datapoints.
    CraftingListener
    Listener that records crafting recipe use.
    CropControlListener  
    CustomCraftingListener
    Listener that records crafting recipe use.
    DropListener
    Contributes player.drop stats when a person drops something

    Contributes block.dispense.TYPE when a dispensor/dropper launches an item.
    FishingListener
    Contributes player.fishing tracking data, records location, player, and item / amount retrieved.
    HiddenOreListener  
    HuntingListener
    Listener that accumulates kills of non-players by players, and players by entities (including players).
    InventoryListener
    Contributes inventory.moveto.TYPE stats when items move to an inventory, paired with Contributes inventory.movefrom.TYPE stats when items leaves an inventory.
    MovementListener
    Example Listener; this sends for aggregation movement data on players.
    PickupListener
    Contributes player.pickup stats when a person picks up something

    Contributes inventory.pickup.TYPE when an inventory holder picks up an item.
    PlaceListener
    Sample Listener class that records all block placements for summation by who and what.
    RedstoneListener
    Contributes the redstone.current.increase and .decrease and .stable datamarkers.
